<!-- ============ HEADER (shared shell) ============ -->

<!-- ============ HERO (Plan C — two-tier) ============ -->
<section class="hero">
  <Svg19 class="botan hero-botan-tl" aria-hidden="true" />
  <Svg20 class="botan hero-botan-br" aria-hidden="true" />
  <div class="hero-inner">
    <p class="eyebrow">Zuo Yue Zi Meal Plan</p>
    <h1>Low Carb Meal</h1>
    <!-- CONFIRM: 減醣月子餐 is used on the current Meal Plans page; no official Chinese name appears on the Order Form -->
    <p class="cn-title">減醣月子餐</p>
    <p class="hero-sub">Recovery, Simplified With Purpose</p>
    <p class="lede">The low-carb lifestyle you live — <em>tailored for Zuo Yue Zi.</em></p>
    <p class="hero-price"><span class="from">30 days · 3 meals a day</span>{usd(products.local_lowcarb_30d.price)}</p>
    <div class="hero-cta">
      <a href="#pricing" class="btn btn-primary">See what's included</a>
      <a href="#taste" class="btn btn-ghost">Try a taste first</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <!-- HERO BANNER IMAGE — a wide, warm shot of a Low Carb day: soups, entrée, vegetables, no rice bowl (~1600×640) -->
  <div class="hero-banner reveal">
    <div class="img-slot">
      <!-- <img src="images/lowcarb-hero.jpg" alt="A Low Carb Meal spread — postpartum soups, entrées and warm vegetables"> -->
      <span class="slot-icon">❀</span>
      <span class="slot-label">Hero Image</span>
      <span class="slot-hint">Wide, warm shot of a Low Carb day — soups, entrée, vegetables · ~1600 × 640</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============ OPENING (names the doubt: "will low carb be warm enough, nourishing enough?") ============ -->
<section class="opening">
  <div class="narrow reveal">
    <p>If low-carb is how you already live, the traditional confinement table can give you pause. All that rice, the porridge, the sweet soups — <em>beautiful, and exactly right for many mothers.</em> Just not quite the way you eat.</p>
    <p>So this plan holds onto the warmth of Zuo Yue Zi — the slow-simmered soups, the ginger and sesame oil, the herbs that follow your month — while easing back the rice, porridge, and sweets.</p>
    <p class="pull">The same Zuo Yue Zi. Just made for a low-carb life.</p>
    <p>It comes out of the same kitchen, follows the same three-stage recovery sequence, and arrives just as hot — three meals a day, built on protein, warm vegetables, and slow-simmered postpartum soups. Nothing dressed up as diet food. Just recovery food, made the way you actually eat.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="floral-divider reveal">
  <span class="line"></span>
  <Svg21 aria-hidden="true" />
  <span class="line r"></span>
</div>

<!-- ============ DAILY ============ -->
<section class="daily" id="daily">
  <Svg22 class="botan daily-botan" aria-hidden="true" />
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="section-head reveal">
      <p class="eyebrow">What Arrives Every Day</p>
      <h2>Everything that heals. Nothing that doesn't.</h2>
      <p>Every day of your thirty days, you'll receive:</p>
    </div>
    <div class="daily-grid reveal">
      <div class="daily-cell">
        <!-- IMAGE — an entrée with warm vegetables, no rice bowl in frame (~600×400) -->
        <div class="img-slot"><span class="slot-icon">❀</span><span class="slot-label">Dish Photo</span><span class="slot-hint">Entrée with warm vegetables · ~600 × 400</span></div>
        <div class="cell-body">
          <div class="num"><span>一</span></div>
          <h3>Three low-carb meals</h3>
          <p>Protein, warm vegetables, and warming herbs at every meal — an egg dish at breakfast, then a full entrée and vegetables at both lunch and dinner. Cooked from scratch, delivered hot.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="daily-cell">
        <!-- IMAGE — a slow-simmered postpartum soup (~600×400) -->
        <div class="img-slot"><span class="slot-icon">❀</span><span class="slot-label">Dish Photo</span><span class="slot-hint">A slow-simmered postpartum soup · ~600 × 400</span></div>
        <div class="cell-body">
          <div class="num"><span>二</span></div>
          <h3>Healing soups at every sitting</h3>
          <p>A fish or lunch soup at midday. The traditional Taiwanese postpartum soup and a dinner soup at night. Simmered for hours, rich in collagen and minerals — this is the warmth the tradition is really built on.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="daily-cell">
        <!-- IMAGE — a plated low-carb day, clean and light (~600×400) -->
        <div class="img-slot"><span class="slot-icon">❀</span><span class="slot-label">Dish Photo</span><span class="slot-hint">A plated Low Carb day · ~600 × 400</span></div>
        <div class="cell-body">
          <div class="num"><span>三</span></div>
          <h3>No rice, grains, or sweet drinks</h3>
          <p>No porridge, no rice bowls, no desserts, no sugary daily drink. It's the leanest of our five plans by design — for lightness and steady energy through the day.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============ GALLERY ============ -->
