  </div>
</section>

<div class="floral-divider reveal">
  <span class="line"></span>
  <Svg21 aria-hidden="true" />
  <span class="line r"></span>
</div>

<!-- ============ PERSONA ============ -->
<section class="persona">
  <Svg23 class="botan persona-botan" aria-hidden="true" />
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="persona-grid reveal">
      <div class="persona-left">
        <p class="eyebrow">Perfect For You If…</p>
        <h2>Honor the tradition. Stay true to yourself.</h2>
        <p>The Low Carb Meal is for the mom who already lives low-carb — and wants the warmth and nourishment of Zuo Yue Zi shaped around the way she eats.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="persona-right">
        <p>Maybe you're managing postpartum blood sugar, or bloating, or an energy dip that shows up an hour after every meal — and you'd rather not spend a month working against that.</p>
        <p>Maybe low-carb is simply how you already eat, and it feels strange to abandon what works for your body at the exact moment your body needs the most from you.</p>
        <p>Or maybe you want strength, not heaviness. You believe in the tradition — you just want a version of it that <em>honors your roots and your goals at the same time</em>.</p>
        <p>Whichever you are, this plan exists so you never have to choose between the two.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

