          <p class="tag">Recovery Booster</p>
          <h3>Slow-Simmered Chicken Essence</h3>
          <p class="cn">熬雞精</p>
          <p>The natural companion to a low-carb month — freshly brewed from <strong>premium aged hens</strong> and simmered for hours until every drop is rich with collagen, protein, and minerals, then concentrated into one small warming cup.</p>
          <p>Pure protein, no sugar, nothing to work around. Easy to sip on the days you're too tired for a full meal — it arrives ready to warm.</p>
          <p class="addon-price">{usd(products.chicken_essence.price)} / serving · add on whenever you like</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="addon-card">
        <!-- IMAGE — the daily herbal drinks (~760×400) -->
        <div class="img-slot"><span class="slot-icon">❀</span><span class="slot-label">Add-on Photo</span><span class="slot-hint">The daily herbal drinks · ~760 × 400</span></div>
        <div class="addon-body">
          <p class="tag">Optional Herbal Add-On</p>
          <h3>The 30-Day Herbal Drinks</h3>
          <p class="cn">月子藥膳</p>
          <p>The daily herbal drinks that have anchored Chinese postpartum recovery for generations — <strong>15 formulas</strong> that follow the traditional recovery sequence, stage by stage across your thirty days. One cup a day.</p>
          <p>They fit this plan naturally: no sugar, no carbs — just the herbal layer of Zuo Yue Zi that the food alone can't carry.</p>
          <p class="addon-price">{usd(products.herbal_drink.price * 30)} / 30 days · 1 cup a day</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

